s can possibly distinguish this scenario with other boosted DM\nmodels or solar axion models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 17:26:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 10:00:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 07:56:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
