e radiated wavefronts, we finally present a\ntime varying IRS concept making use of a time-delay based approach relying on a\ndelay adjustment between the reflection coefficients of the IRS' unit cell\nlattices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 22:05:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
