an noise-based method when unmodeled\ndynamics are present, in terms of both parameter estimation error and Regret\nobtained using the parameter estimates with a Linear Quadratic Regulator in\nfeedback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 01:20:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2022 17:19:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-17"}
